description:
Filling in for Colin, Doug Gottlieb discusses the game plan of the Miami Dolphins, the ongoing Ezekiel Elliott situation, NFL GMs, and the difference between the Chargers and the Cowboys. Guests include Chris Spielman, Brock Huard, and Mike Sando.
